Package org.zoolu.sip.transaction

Interface Summary
AckTransactionServerListener A AckTransactionServerListener listens for AckTransactionServer onTransAckTimeout(AckTransactionServer) events.
InviteTransactionServerListener A TransactionServerListener listens for InviteTransactionServer events.
TransactionClientListener A TransactionClientListener listens for TransactionClient events.
TransactionServerListener A TransactionServerListener listens for TransactionServer events.
 

Class Summary
AckTransactionClient ACK client transaction should follow an INVITE client transaction within an INVITE Dialog in a SIP UAC.
AckTransactionServer ACK server transaction should follow an INVITE server transaction within an INVITE Dialog in a SIP UAC.
InviteTransactionClient INVITE client transaction as defined in RFC 3261 (Section 17.2.1).
InviteTransactionServer INVITE server transaction as defined in RFC 3261 (Section 17.2.1).
Transaction Abstract class Transaction is hinerited by classes ClientTransaction, ServerTransaction, InviteClientTransaction and InviteServerTransaction.
TransactionClient Generic client transaction as defined in RFC 3261 (Section 17.1.2).
TransactionServer Generic server transaction as defined in RFC 3261 (Section 17.2.2).
